{"tid":1481992,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「更正」2點維園見 - 熱門冇任何行動post 求資訊圖","createTime":"2019-08-18T02:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T04:19:38.000Z","uid":196227,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e24a5bb95368e90c0049f6f541a005713e716f9a","tid":1481992,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:46:16.000Z","msg":"以往每次大型集會都一堆路線圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n響應既店鋪名<br />\n休息地點<br />\n文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n但係今日咩都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以有人入黎放低所知資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等今日可以順順利利<br />\n<br />\n唔好再放飛機文，今日完咗大把時間放<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係資訊圖可以令人安心知邊道有得休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港、時代革命<br />\n2點維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ad76334a463ffeeb70a96f5f53190250cfdaae","tid":1481992,"uid":196227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:49:24.000Z","msg":"求資訊圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368e205bdc660aa54fff68341025f05d9e146697","tid":1481992,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:51:17.000Z","msg":"2點維園見，希望各位推其他行動post<br />\n唔好再打飛機<br />\n<a href=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/DeNHo39.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDeNHo39.png&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1Kcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=9ae5a315\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/DeNHo39.png</a>"},{"pid":"5366a08e45eb8272c4542a965fcc2e7ee5e9d905","tid":1481992,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na